    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔呼吁提供通胀回落的证据，美国国债价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/treasuries-slip-as-powell-calls-for-evidence-of-inflation-s-ebb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向华盛顿立法者表示，他希望获得更多通胀降温的证据，这增强了市场对今年降息的预期，导致美国国债价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/treasuries-slip-as-powell-calls-for-evidence-of-inflation-s-ebb</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦赞同鲍威尔的观点，称劳动力市场通胀压力已减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-echoes-powell-saying-labor-market-now-less-inflationary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，劳动力市场不再像疫情复苏初期那样推动美国经济通胀，这与美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔早些时候的评论相呼应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-echoes-powell-saying-labor-market-now-less-inflationary</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:19:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔认为巴塞尔协议 III 的修订取得了进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-sees-progress-on-changes-to-basel-iii-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，巴塞尔协议 III 修订案将在大约 60 天内公布，供大家评论。鲍威尔在参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会作证时发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-sees-progress-on-changes-to-basel-iii-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:15:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通交易部门警告称，标普 500 指数将因 CPI 波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/jpmorgan-s-trading-desk-warns-s-p-500-will-turn-volatile-on-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通交易部门发出警告称，在经历了一段长期的平静期后，投资者应该为本周股市的波动做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/jpmorgan-s-trading-desk-warns-s-p-500-will-turn-volatile-on-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称更多良好通胀数据将增强美联储信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-says-more-good-inflation-data-would-strengthen-fed-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，最近的数据表明物价“进一步温和上涨”，但“更多好数据”将增强人们对通胀正在向美联储 2% 目标下降的信心。鲍威尔在参议院银行、住房和城市事务委员会作证时发表了上述讲话（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-09/powell-says-more-good-inflation-data-would-strengthen-fed-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:09:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>知情人士透露，图利普·西迪克将出任英国城市事务大臣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 为英国金融城大臣，该职位属于财政部，将让她成为监管和倡导关键金融服务行业的核心人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
