    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔发表“平衡”观点后股市保持涨势：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于华尔街认为杰罗姆·鲍威尔的经济言论是平衡的，股市徘徊在历史高位附近，这加强了人们对美联储今年将能够降息的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
